casebody.head_matter:
Antone L. KNOX, petitioner,
v.
OKLAHOMA PARDON AND PAROLE BOARD, et al.
No. 16-8184.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 15, 2017.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
